quran[10{c,v,t}:
16,55,"taakay Allah ke ahsaan ki nashukri kere acha, mazay kar lau, anqareeb tumhe maloom ho jaye ga"
16,56,"yeh log jin ki haqeeqat se waaqif nahi hain unn ke hissay hamaray diye hue rizaq mein se muqarrar karte hain khuda ki qasam, zaroor tum se poocha jaye ga ke yeh jhoot tum ne kaisay ghurr liye thay ?"
16,57,yeh khuda ke liye betiyan tajweez karte hain subhan Allah ! aur inn ke liye woh jo yeh khud chahain ?
16,58,jab inn mein se kisi ko beti ke peda honay ki khush khaberi di jati hai to uss ke chehray par clons(ghum ki sihyai) chhaa jati hai aur woh bas khoon ka sa ghoont pi kar reh jata hai
16,59,logon se chupta phirta hai ke iss buri khabar ke baad kya kisi ko mun dukhaay sochta hai ke zillat ke sath beti ko liye rahay ya matti mein daba day? dekho kaisay buray hukum hain jo yeh khuda ke baray mein lagatay hain
16,60,"buri sifaat se mutsif kiye jaane ke Laiq to woh log hain jo akhirat ka yaqeen nahi rakhtay raha Allah , to uss ke liye sab se bartar sifaat hain, wohi to sab par ghalib aur hikmat mein kaamil hai"
16,61,"agar kahin Allah logon ko unn ki zayad-ti par foran hi pakar liya kar taa to roye zameen par kisi mutnaqas ko nah chhorta lekin woh sab ko aik waqt muqarrar taq mohlat deta hai, phir jab woh waqt aa jata hai to is se koi aik gharri bhar bhi agay peechay nahi ho sakta"
16,62,"aaj yeh log woh cheezein Allah ke liye tajweez kar rahay hain jo khud apne liye aِnhin napasand hain, aur jhoot kehti hain inn ki zubanain ke inn ke liye bhala hi bhala hai inn ke liye to aik hi cheez hai, aur woh hai dozakh ki aag zaroor yeh sab se pehlay uss mein p_hnchaye jayen ge"
16,63,"khuda ki qasam, ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum se pehlay bhi bohat si qomon mein hum rasool bhaij chuke hain ( aur pehlay bhi yahi hota raha hai ke ) shetan ne unn ke buray kartoot unhen khushnuma bana kar dukhaay ( aur Rasolo-n ki baat unhon ne maan kar nah di ) wohi shetan aaj inn logon ka bhi sarparast bana howa hai aur yeh dard naak saza ke mustahiq ban rahay hain"
16,64,hum ne yeh kitaab tum par is liye nazil ki hai ke tum unn ikhtilafat ki haqeeqat inn par khol do jin mein yeh parre hue hain yeh kitaab rahnumai aur rehmat ban kar utri hai unn logon ke liye jo isay maan len
